A. Stored XSS
B. Reflected XSS
C. DOM-based XSS
D. Blind XSS

24. Authentication bypass using ' OR 1=1 -- works because:
A. SQL ignores WHERE clause
B. Condition always evaluates true
C. Password hashing fails
D. Session expires

25. Which defense is MOST effective against SQL Injection?
A. Input filtering
B. Parameterized queries
C. Web Application Firewall
D. Escaping characters

26. An attacker injects <script> into feedback form and it executes for all users. This is:
A. Reflected XSS
B. DOM XSS
C. Stored XSS
D. Blind XSS

27. Why are stored procedures NOT automatically secure?
A. They run on server
B. They can contain dynamic SQL
C. They are encrypted
D. They are compiled

